[30;1m50 | [0m[35mdef _trunc_normal_(tensor, mean, std, a, b):[0m
[30;1m51 | [0m[35m    # Cut & paste from PyTorch official master until it's in a few official releases - RW[0m
[30;1m52 | [0m[35m    # Method based on https://people.sc.fsu.edu/~jburkardt/presentations/truncated_normal.pdf[0m
[30;1m53 | [0m[35m    def norm_cdf(x):[0m
